#Market News January 26, 2018 / 10:37 PM / in 20 minutes BRIEF-Starboard Value Says Starboard V&O Fund Delivered Letter To Stewart Information Services Nominating Slate Of 3 Director Candidates Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Jan 26 (Reuters) - Stewart Information Services Corp : 
* STARBOARD VALUE LP SAYS ON JAN 26, STARBOARD V&O FUND DELIVERED A LETTER TO STEWART INFORMATION SERVICES NOMINATING SLATE OF 3 DIRECTOR CANDIDATES Source text - bit.ly/2ndNTBY Further company coverage:
